[h3 id=BossHealth 
	" Boss Health
	$LF
]h3
[p 
	"Boss HP can only drop 1 HP per frame.  This means the strategy isn't as much about unloading bullets as fast as possible, but instead trying to make sure damage is registered every frame.
	$LF
	[br 
	]br
	$LF
]p
